  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting Conflict-Affected Populations in Cameroon through the Implementation of the Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In order to support evidence-based and accountable service provision by humanitarian partners in Cameroon, IOM plans to continue collecting, processing and disseminating information on displacement trends and most pressing sectoral needs of conflict-affected populations in the North-West, South-West (NWSW) regions, and Far-North regions of the country, through its Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM).</narrative>
  </description>
